Stay quiet.

7
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:22,841
If you tell people, I'm going to get you.

8
00:01:26,886 --> 00:01:29,809
That's Ro Bin, isn't it?

9
00:01:34,515 --> 00:01:36,316
Seo Ro Bin!

10
00:01:55,074 --> 00:01:56,916
Is this a hamburger shop?

11
00:01:56,916 --> 00:01:58,978
I told you to stay out of my business.

12
00:02:01,250 --> 00:02:03,793
- So this is why you can't tell anyone?
- Let go.

13
00:02:05,925 --> 00:02:08,908
